<li><a href="./itom/Operations_Bridge:2019.05/ChConOpsB" title="Operations Bridge:2019.05/ChConOpsB">Check connectivity</a></li>
<li><a href="./itom/Operations_Bridge:2019.05/TaGrOpsB" title="Operations Bridge:2019.05/TaGrOpsB">Target group</a></li>
